race.comment: CALYX ROSE (3) has been out of the winners list for a while but does look well placed here. Turned in a better run latest and drawn to have every chance first try at the mile. BIKER (1) was a second-up winner here at the mile when hitting the line hard. Fitter again and looks tough to stop again. SEACRYPTION (6) is going better than form suggests. Suited here and will be hitting the line hard. SPELLMASTER (2) has drawn out but has the pace to overcome the draw. Extra trip a plus and drops in weight. Will give a sight. PEAKING TOM (5) has finished fourth at last two but both runs have been sound. Another who will be winding up late.
